history.content:
Interested in using machine learning to help patients? Alife Health uses AI to help improve IVF and is a fully remote, Silicon Valley-based company backed by investors that include 23andMe, Intuitive Surgical, and Accel Partners.
Alife Health will be hosting an event with UC Berkeley SWE on Tuesday, April 6th from 5-6 PM through their Startup Spring series. Come to participate in a presentation/Q&A from their founder and company representatives; they will also be discussing open positions.

Link to their open roles: https://www.alifehealth.com/jobs 

Link to event page: https://fb.me/e/BUzEbpuj
